<h1 id="track-time-off-for-the-family-and-medical-leave-act-fmla" sourcefile="fin-ops-core/fin-ops/hr/localizations/noam-usa-track-time-for-fmla.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">Track time off for the Family and Medical Leave Act (FMLA)</h1>


<p sourcefile="fin-ops-core/fin-ops/hr/localizations/noam-usa-track-time-for-fmla.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">This article explains how to track Family and Medical Leave Act (FMLA) eligibility and hours that are worked to meet federal requirements.</p>
